title: Vegab
typeOfFood: Vegan, Italian, Organic, Mediterranean, Fast food, Take-out, Fusion, Middle Eastern
description: Vegan fast food restaurant est. 2015 in the city center. Features a plant-based kebab made from tofu. Also on the menu are hot dogs, zapiekanki, lasagna, and cakes; weekly dishes and soup specials; smoothies made with hemp milk, goji berries, chia, barley grass and other ingredients. Kitchen makes plant milks fresh daily.
